2. Languages & Standards
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
  - C++17          — core networking engine, packet parsing, caching
  - Python 3.10+   — API layer, fallback resolver, metrics
  - HTML5 / CSS3   — dashboard markup and dark glassmorphism UI
  - Vanilla JS ES6 — frontend logic (no frameworks)
  - RFC 1035       — DNS Implementation and Specification
  - RFC 1034       — DNS Concepts and Facilities

