3. Core Libraries & APIs
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
C++ Standard Library:
  <winsock2.h> / <sys/socket.h>  — UDP and TCP socket I/O
  <ws2tcpip.h>                   — inet_addr, sockaddr_in
  <chrono>                       — high-resolution timing (latency_ms)
  <random>                       — transaction ID + root-server selection
  <mutex>, <list>, <map>         — thread-safe LRU cache
  <sstream>, <iomanip>           — JSON serialisation without dependencies

Python stdlib:
  socket, struct   — raw UDP packet build + send for fallback resolver
  subprocess       — spawn C++ binary, capture stdout/stderr
  threading        — cache lock, Flask thread mode, browser-open timer
  collections      — OrderedDict (LRU cache), deque (metrics ring buffer)
  random           — transaction ID in fallback_resolve()
  time             — TTL expiry calculation

Python packages (requirements.txt):
  Flask 2.3.0+     — REST API framework
  flask-cors 4.0+  — CORS headers for browser dashboard
  requests         — used in test suite (not in production path)

